cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with the registration of 3D point clouds, which is a common task in computer vision. It may also belong to the robotics (cs.RO) sub-category as point cloud registration is important for robot perception and navigation. The use of machine learning techniques suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. Finally, the paper may also belong to the graphics (cs.GR) sub-category as point cloud registration is important for 3D modeling and rendering.
